  "text": "The frame system A in (3.17) can be chosen to be independent of the convolution kernel H s . Hence, this approach does not model the deconvolution by an inpainting problem in a transform domain. As it is proven in [CITATION_1] , the sequenceṽ n converges. Letṽ be its limit, then the solution v is defined to be A * ṽ . The limit is a minimizer of the following cost functional",
